(1728, 'Sam Altman returns as CEO, OpenAI has a new initial board', 'Mira Murati as CTO, Greg Brockman returns as President. Read messages from CEO Sam Altman and board chair Bret Taylor.', 1701244800, 6, 'https://openai.com/blog/sam-altman-returns-as-ceo-openai-has-a-new-initial-board', 1713122732),
